name: Paxos Gold from Ethereum
description: Bridged from Ethereum via https://bridge.pulsechain.com. Original Address - 0x45804880De22913dAFE09f4980848ECE6EcbAf78. PAX Gold (PAXG) is a digital asset where one token is backed by one fine troy ounce (t oz) of a 400 oz London Good Delivery gold bar, stored in Brink’s gold vaults.
